These six values create a comprehensive framework that speaks directly to how technical founders think, work, and evaluate partnerships. They bridge the gap between technical excellence and business success in a language that technical leaders inherently understand and respect.

The sequence flows from understanding buyers to delivering outcomes that create authentic market resonance.
